 hybrid will start in the third quarter of 2010, six months later than we (and his customers) were led to believe.\nFisker basically blames it on the current global financial troubles. People came in late with money, or didnt come in at [...]\n\n\nRelated posts:Corkscrew Karma: Fisker Karma Set to Drive onto the Scene at Laguna Seca2010 Fisker Karma: Fisker Testing and Taking Orders2009 Fisker Karma  Official Photos and Info...<br><a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/caranddriver/blog/~3/ZUjgyOj20tk/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feedproxy.google.com</a><br>','Fisker Slides Backward, Delays Karma'),(2105,'3','2009-12-04 17:39:42','<img src=\"http://www.bmwblog.com/wp-content/uploads/BMW_M3_Coupe_06-655x491.jpg\" alt=\"BMW_M3_Coupe_photo\" />BMW   announced today that it has won two Best Resale Value awards from   Kelley Blue Book ......<br><a href=\"http://www.bmwblog.com/2009/12/04/bmw-models-praised-for-resale-value-by-kbb/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.bmwblog.com</a><br>','BMW Models Praised for Resale Value by KBB'),(2106,'3','2009-12-04 19:05:35','\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nGeneral Motors and Suzukis relationship dates as far back as 1981, but a post-bankruptcy era and a struggling market have forced the two apart. GM and Suzukis joint Canadian plant has now been obtained solely by GM.\n\nGM first began its quest for a partnership with Suzuki in 1981 when it obtained a 5.3 percent stake [...]\n\n\n...<br><a href=\"http://feeds.leftlanenews.com/click.phdo?i=5870f638b4bd347e879e7bdd8f65379c\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: feeds.leftlanenews.com</a><br>','GM and Suzuki to end CAMI partnership'),(2107,'3','2009-12-04 18:24:03','\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFollowing the departing of GMs CEO, Fritz Henderson, high-profile vice chairmen Bob Lutz will receive new duties and titles. GM has also named Lutz replacement for his marketing roles, Susan Docherty.\n\nVice chairmen Bob Lutz is no stranger to the spotlight at GM, and now Lutz has been shifted from hi