ee the light of day. But these variations are both around [...]...<br><a href=\"http://www.4wheelsnews.com/gm-will-not-build-a-convertible-version-of-the-cadillac-cts/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.4wheelsnews.com</a><br>','GM will not build a convertible version of the Cadillac CTS'),(2129,'3','2009-12-04 19:57:21','BMW AGs global unit sales are expected to increase in December after having had a high single-digit percentage rise in November, according to CEO Norbert Reithofer.\nThe worlds biggest premium carmaker said that the improvement in unit sales shows a slim rise in demand for luxury vehicles. It can be recalled that near the height of [...]...<br><a href=\"http://www.4wheelsnews.com/bmw-global-unit-sales-grow-by-a-high-single-digit-percentage-in-november/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.4wheelsnews.com</a><br>','Bmw global unit sales grow by a high single-digit percentage in November'),(2130,'3','2009-12-04 19:45:07','Ford Motor Co.s business plan will not entail relying on having had its first U.S. market share gain since 1995. Ford was reported to have gained 1 percentage point of retail share in the California market but it isnt expecting that trend to continue. Jim Farley, group vice president of global marketing, said that the [...]...<br><a href=\"http://www.4wheelsnews.com/ford-to-see-its-first-us-market-share-gain-since-1995/\" target=\"_blank\">Fuente Original: www.4wheelsnews.com</a><br>','Ford to see its first U.S. market share gain since 1995'),(2131,'3','2009-12-04 19:42:47','<img src=\"http://blog.caranddriver.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/2010-Dodge-Viper-SRT10-ACR-Nurburgring-03-440x268.jpg\" alt=\"2010 Dodge Viper SRT10 ACR Nürburgring\" />\nTucked back in a dark corner of the 2009 L.A. auto show was a snake pit containing five vicious Vipers harnessing enough horsepower and torque to pull the convention center off its foundation.\nEasily overlooked as just a few race cars and production Vipers, we wandered over to